<header>
  <img src="/assets/progression-series-logo-v0.png" />
  <h1>Turku Cardsports Pokémon TCG Progression Series!</h1>
</header>

<main>
  <div class="intro">
    <p>
      A <strong>Pokémon TCG Progression Series</strong> is a format where we
      open half a booster box (16 boosters) from each set from the block one at
      a time, starting with Scarlet and Violet base set. After each set, we
      build a 60-card deck from what we've pulled so far, battle against each
      other and repeat for every set in the block.
    </p>
    <p>
      It's a format that challenges deckbuilding skills and gives us a reason to
      play with cards we would otherwise not play with (or even have read
      before).
    </p>
  </div>

  <hr />

  <h2>Total ({{series | finishedSeries}} sets finished)</h2>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Games</th>
        <th>Wins</th>
        <th>Losses</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {% for player in collections.ranking %}
      <tr>
        <td>{{player.playerName}}</td>
        <td>{{player.stats.games}}</td>
        <td>{{player.stats.wins}}</td>
        <td>{{player.stats.losses}}</td>
      </tr>
      {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <hr />
  {% for serie in series %}

  <h2>{{serie.name}} ({{serie.ongoing | ongoing}})</h2>

  <h3>Ranking</h3>

  {{ collections.series | log }} {{ serie.id | log}}
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Games</th>
        <th>Wins</th>
        <th>Losses</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {% for player in collections.series[serie.id].table %}
      <tr>
        <td>{{player.playerName}}</td>
        <td>{{player.stats.games}}</td>
        <td>{{player.stats.wins}}</td>
        <td>{{player.stats.losses}}</td>
      </tr>
      {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <details>
    <summary><h3>Matchups</h3></summary>
    <ul>
      {% for match in collections.series[serie.id].matches %}
      <li>{{match}}</li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    {% endfor %}
  </details>
</main>

